<div style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">25.</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.5pt">清李榕《华岳志》卷四第十四页。 </span></div>
